title: Zoom Freak 4 "Greek Coastline"
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Giannis is an incessant storm of stamina and skill that keeps coming at opponents for 4 quarters or more. The forward-thinking design of his latest signature shoe helps propel you down the court in a lightweight fit that moves with you. It can handle quick changes in direction on both sides of the floor, giving you side-to-side stability and multidirectional traction as you Euro step to the hoop. The colors pay tribute to 1 of the Greek Freak’s favorite coastal getaway spots, in the country he proudly calls home.
label: IN_STOCK
